para_sentences.para_0: Algorithms are an important topic to crack any technical coding interview round. Taking the algorithms course is one part of it. Mastering the topics takes a different level of commitment. To assist in this journey of completing this course successfully and gaining confidence in learning and mastering algorithms hearing from those who have successfully completed this process would add tremendous value and inspiration.
para_sentences.para_1: Below is a short sharing from alumni of OSU on their journey of starting as novice in the computer science and algorithms topics to gaining a job that they cherish.

para_sentences.para_0: Kejo Hsieh has done her Masters in Computer Science from Oregon State University. As of 2021, Kejo is working as a Software Engineer at Amazon. Kejo shares a short recording on practicing algorithms.
